---
import BaseLayout from "../components/layout/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="图源与导出说明" description="贡献者如何命名、导出和复用交互图源。">
  <main class="chapter-main">
    <p class="eyebrow">Diagram Source</p>
    <h1 class="page-title">图源与导出说明</h1>
    <p class="lede">
      本项目的图解需要截图友好、可维护、可绑定交互状态。优先使用手工整理的 SVG，并遵循稳定 id 约定。
    </p>

    <section class="section-band" aria-labelledby="export-flow">
      <p class="eyebrow">推荐流程</p>
      <h2 id="export-flow">从图源到可交互 SVG</h2>
      <div class="pill-grid">
        <div class="pill">Figma / Excalidraw 草图</div>
        <div class="pill">导出 SVG</div>
        <div class="pill">SVGO 优化</div>
        <div class="pill">补 id / data-role</div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-band" aria-labelledby="naming">
      <p class="eyebrow">SVG 命名规范</p>
      <h2 id="naming">稳定命名让动画和测试更可靠</h2>
      <div class="demo-grid">
        <div class="demo-card"><strong>node-*</strong><p>概念节点、流程节点、token 节点。</p></div>
        <div class="demo-card"><strong>arrow-*</strong><p>数据流、控制流、影响关系。</p></div>
        <div class="demo-card"><strong>label-*</strong><p>截图和导出时保留的文字标签。</p></div>
        <div class="demo-card"><strong>highlight-*</strong><p>当前步骤、失败状态、解决状态。</p></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-band" aria-labelledby="downloads">
      <p class="eyebrow">可复用图源</p>
      <h2 id="downloads">下载首批 SVG 源文件</h2>
      <div class="demo-grid overview-grid">
        <a class="demo-card" href="/diagrams/rag-pipeline.svg" download aria-label="下载 RAG Pipeline SVG">
          <span>SVG</span>
          <strong>下载 RAG Pipeline SVG</strong>
          <p>包含 <code>node-query</code>、<code>arrow-query-embedding</code> 等稳定 id，便于绑定交互状态。</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-band" aria-labelledby="screenshots">
      <p class="eyebrow">截图友好</p>
      <h2 id="screenshots">每张图都应该能单独传播</h2>
      <p>
        保持边距、标题、激活状态和简化说明清晰可见。导出或截图前，优先选择能表达一个核心 aha moment 的状态，
        避免把多个控件面板、过长解释和复杂参数同时放进画面。
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
